The Internet in China is highly restricted, most Western social media websites are blocked. Purchase a reliable proxy before travelling!
You’ll be fine traveling alone even at night as a girl when you’re in populated area.Since there’re a bunch of cameras. Enjoy your trip
Beijing currently has two airport, all international airlines land at Beijing capital international airport. It’s somewhere at the outskirts of Beijing. If you’re on budget, you can take airport express train to downtown, it’s 25RMB for a single ticket.